snippet.title: Tabletop Simulator VR Trailer
snippet.description:
Tabletop Simulator now supports VR with the HTC Vive! VR is currently in beta.

http://store.steampowered.com/app/286160

DLCs shown in the video:
Zombicide - http://store.steampowered.com/app/468726
Euphoria - http://store.steampowered.com/app/417300
Superfight - http://store.steampowered.com/app/367330
Scythe - http://store.steampowered.com/app/446980
Cosmic Encounter - http://store.steampowered.com/app/405130

Music: (Both songs can be found in the Youtube Audio Library)
Court of the Queen - Music to Delight by Kevin MacLeod is licensed under a Creative Commons Attribution license (https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/)
Source: http://incompetech.com/music/royalty-free/index.html?isrc=USUAN1100728
Artist: http://incompetech.com

Invisible by Vibe Tracks

Special thanks to Gikerl for participating in the video!
